---
title: Sweet 'n' Sticky Tofu Stir-Fry with Red Bell Pepper and Sugar Snap Peas
description: You'll feel like you've been transported to the streets of Beijing when you taste this fragrant stir-fry. The combination of hoisin sauce, ginger and chili-garlic is a classic and fool-proof combination that flavours the tofu and vegetables brilliantly. Yum!
